OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers,
OL,6,Fsome heavy, will clear from the west
OL,7,Fduring the evening. This will leave
OL,8,Fthe night dry with increasing clear
OL,9,Fspells, these leading to frost patches
OL,10,Ftowards morning.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FThe morning will begin dry
OL,13,Fwith sunny spells and a patchy frost.
OL,14,FCloud will spread northeast during the
OL,15,Fmorning. Outbreaks of rain, some
OL,16,Fheavy, spread northeast later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
