OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FBands
OL,6,Fof rain push northeast with showers,
OL,7,Fsome heavy and thundery, following
OL,8,FWednesday. These showers continue
OL,9,FThursday morning. A further rain band
OL,10,Fpushes northeast Friday, showers
OL,11,Ffollow later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
